org.apache.chemistry.opencmis.commons.impl.json.parser

Class JSONParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.chemistry.opencmis.commons.impl.json.parser.JSONParser

  • public class JSONParser
extends Object
    Parser for JSON text. Please note that JSONParser is NOT thread-safe. (Taken from JSON.simple and modified for OpenCMIS.)
    Author:
    FangYidong

        Parameters:
        in -
